          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Defense of Legal Workers Act of 2015</strong></p> <p> Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to: (1) exclude from the definition of &quot;unauthorized alien,&quot; with respect to the unlawful employment of aliens, any alien otherwise admitted to and lawfully present in the United States; and (2) consider an alien without lawful status to be an unauthorized alien whose employment is unlawful.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2015-01-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
